text: Ancita penicillata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1917. It is known from Australia.BioLib.cz - Ancita penicillata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ancita Category:Beetles described in 1917
